			"The fourth line, divided, shows its subject enriching the family.  There will be great good fortune.<br/>\n<br/>\nThe family is enriched, and there is great good fortune: this is due to the docility belonging to the subject of the line, and its being in its correct place.\n",
			"The fourth line, divided, shows all occasion for repentance in its subject passed away.  He takes game for its threefold use in his hunting.<br/>\n<br/>\nHe takes game in his hunting, enough for the threefold use of it:  he achieves merit.\n",
